=NIAC Meeting - September 2007=
The next meeting of the  [[NIAC | NeXus International Advisory Committee]] will be held at the [http://www.hmi.de Hahn-Meitner-Institut] in Berlin, Germany. The meeting is planned for September 24-26, 2007.

== Accommodation ==
Accommodation will be at the HMI guest-house on the [http://www.hmi.de/hmi/standorte_en.html#Wannsee HMI campus Wannsee]. The rate for a single room is for the first overnight stay 34€ and 24€ for every following one (double room 52€/34€). [[User:Jens-Uwe Hoffmann | Jens-Uwe Hoffmann]] [mailto:hoffmann-j@hmi.de] is you local contact for reservation and access authorization, please send your name, address and your '''passport number'''. 


Arriving information [http://www.hmi.de/hmi/wegwannsee_en.html to Berlin Wannsee].


== Conference Fee ==

We plan a conference fee of about 100€ per person for coffee, lunch, etc.


